snippet.title: PS1 - Spec Ops Ranger Elite - Full Walkthrough [1080P]🔴
snippet.description:
PS1 - Spec Ops Ranger Elite - Full Walkthrough [1080P]

Spec Ops: Ranger Elite is a third-person squad-based tactical shooter released on April 29th, 2001. This was one of the last in the Spec Ops series before it took a 9 year hiatus. The game, as aforementioned, is played from a third-person perspective. The player takes control of the squad "leader," and one back-up squadmate.  
Source - specops.fandom

 I used to play this game a lot but I do not remember what to do in it how to complete every task in the mission but as game goes  I would say it is an ok game for its time, I can play this game even now it sortoff did not lost its appeal for me only thing I do not like is that they do not give a lot of information on how to complete all the tasks
